					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13332407#post-4663373</guid>
				<title>Re: -1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13332407/scp-5915#post-4663373</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2020 00:16:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Whattman</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3108559</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I feel like basically anything that didn't cause the real world deaths of so many people and so recently could work, but I wouldn't go so far as to actually change anything. It's well written and has a nice gross out factor to it. I admitted upfront that my opinion was biased because I personally know a lot of people from New Orleans who lost loved ones, and the imagery you used here just made me queasy. I very, very rarely downvote anything on this site, so I felt I should give my reasoning behind it, and I may have even overreacted by using words like &quot;disrespectful.&quot; Insensitive sure, but whatever, it's a horror site. Good luck on your future articles.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
