					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49FB9hhoO6c">Where is my mind?</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49FB9hhoO6c">Where is my mind?</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49FB9hhoO6c">Where is my mind?</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49FB9hhoO6c">Way out in the water</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49FB9hhoO6c">See it swimmin'</a></em></p> </div> <hr /> <p>This skip was written after I said something to the effect of my idiot brain vacating it's stupid prison. Weryllium drew comparisons to the humble hermit crab, and then I wrote this instead of collabing with Weryllium because, in his words, &quot;collabing is for nerds&quot;.</p> <p><strong>Valued Critters:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589867095" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" >cybersqyd</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589867095" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ezekieraltavista" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589867095" alt="EzekierAltavista" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ezekieraltavista" >EzekierAltavista</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589867095" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span></p> <p>And thank you for reading.</p> <hr /> <p>Interested in my other works? You can find them <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rtme-author">here</a>.</p> 
